npm run preview  # Preview production build
npm run lint     # ESLint check (js, jsx files)
```

## Critical Rules

### ✅ DO
- Use JSX only (this is NOT a TypeScript project)
- Import icons ONLY from `lucide-react`
- Use CSS variables for colors: `rgb(var(--navigator))`
- Respect the section-based folder structure
- Follow the Navigator design metaphor naming

### ❌ DON'T
- Don't add TypeScript files or types
- Don't use other icon libraries (Font Awesome, Heroicons, etc.)
- Don't use inline colors - use CSS variables or Tailwind classes
- Don't create components outside the established structure
- Don't use class components - hooks only

